headline: Cogent (CCOI) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of internet service provider Cogent Communications (NASDAQ:CCOI) jumped 8.1% in the afternoon session after it received a double upgrade from Wells Fargo, which cited a favorable risk/reward outlook.
